the taiwanese capital of taipei 
taiwanese officials refused to allow him to return to taiwan 
because people charged with sedition are not allowed to enter the 
country under the national security law which replaced martial 
rule last july 
taiwan had been under martial law since 1949 when the 
nationalist chinese lost a mainland civil war with the communists 
fled to the island and established a government 
